<section class="vision-section">
    <div class="vision-text">
        <h1>Our Vision</h1>
        <p>At Peraminder, we empower everyone to take control of their finances with ease, clarity, and confidence—dahil bawat piso ay mahalaga. <em>Wala nang stress, wala nang kalituhan!</em> Just simple, clear, and effective financial tracking that works for you. <br /><br />With every expense and goal in check, we help you stay on top of your finances, giving you the freedom to focus on what truly matters. Our goal is to guide you towards financial freedom, so you can live a happy, stress-free life, with your money working for you every step of the way.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vision-image"></div>
</section>

<section class="mission-section">
    <div class="mission-image"></div>
    <div class="mission-text">
        <h1>Our Mission</h1>
        <p>At Peraminder, we aim to simplify financial management for everyone, making it easy to track, save, and grow your money. <em>Tulungan ka namin magtagumpay sa iyong financial journey!</em> With our tools and insights, we make managing your finances a breeze, so you can focus on living your best life. <br /><br />Our mission is to provide you with the tools, knowledge, and support to achieve financial stability and success, so you can live a life free of financial worries and full of possibilities.</p>
    </div>
</section>

